trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <see cref="E:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.ChildChanged" /> and <see cref="E:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.ChildChanged" /> events.
trans-unit.target: 提供 <see cref="E:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.ChildChanged" /> 和 <see cref="E:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.ChildChanged" /> 事件的資料。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ChildChangedEventArgs> class is used by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost> classes when the values of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> or <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.Child%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> properties change.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ChildChangedEventArgs>類別會由<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost>和<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost>類別時的值<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>或<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.Child%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>屬性變更。

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ChildChangedEventArgs.PreviousChild%2A> property to get the previously assigned child control or element.
trans-unit.target: 使用<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ChildChangedEventArgs.PreviousChild%2A>屬性來取得之前指派的子控制項或元素。

trans-unit.source: The value of the <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child" /> property before the new value was assigned.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child" /> 屬性在指派新值以前的值。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ChildChangedEventArgs" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ChildChangedEventArgs" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: Gets the value of the <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child" /> property before the new value was assigned.
trans-unit.target: 取得 <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child" /> 屬性在指派新值以前的值。

trans-unit.source: The value of the <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child" /> property before the new value was assigned.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child" /> 屬性在指派新值以前的值。
